## 1. 🛡️ Security Audit

### ✅ Strengths

**A. Credential Management**
- All sensitive data in [.env](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/.env) (gitignored)
- Environment variables properly injected via Docker
- HuggingFace token added with read-only permissions
- Production credentials clearly separated from dev defaults

**B. Data Integrity**
- `UNIQUE` constraint on [object_key](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/core/ingestion_jobs.py#22-27) prevents duplicate embeddings
- Database transactions properly committed
- Worker retries (3 attempts) prevent partial failures

**C. Input Validation**
- File type validation in [minio_utils.py](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/utils/minio_utils.py)
- Image preprocessing handles corrupt files gracefully
- MinIO webhook signature validation via `WEBHOOK_SECRET`

### ⚠️ Known Gaps (By Design per User Request)

**API Authentication:** **DISABLED**
- **Risk Level:** Medium (if exposed publicly)
- **Mitigation:** OMS handles perimeter auth, service is internal-only
- **Status:** Accepted risk, documented in OMS integration plan

