- ✅ Handles PDF/AI files with white background composite
- ✅ Graceful fallback for corrupt images
- ✅ GIF first-frame extraction

**[ingestion_jobs.py](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/core/ingestion_jobs.py)**
- ✅ 3-retry logic with exponential backoff
- ✅ Thumbnail generation for non-image files
- ✅ Infinite recursion prevention (skips `.thumbnails/`)

### B. Configuration Consistency

**Development ([.env](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/.env))**
```properties
POSTGRES_HOST=127.0.0.1  ← Correct for local uvicorn
REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379/0  ← Correct for local
POSTGRES_PORT=5434  ← Custom port to avoid conflicts
```

**Production ([docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/docker-compose.yml))**
```yaml
POSTGRES_HOST: db  ← Override for container networking
REDIS_URL: redis://redis:6379/0  ← Override for containers
```

✅ **No conflicts detected.** Clear separation between local and Docker environments.

